Date: Tue, 31 Mar 2026 01:59:28 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 08/16] UI: Implement Termux-specific system integrations and
 overrides

- frontend/oauth: Implemented local file fallback for Twitch and YouTube
  API keys (~/.config/obs-studio/*). Bypasses the need for official
  obfuscated build keys.
- frontend/widgets: Replaced QDesktopServices::openUrl with a custom
  TermuxOpenUrl() shell execution (xdg-open). Bypasses Qt D-Bus
  dependencies which are unavailable in the Termux environment.
- frontend/OBSApp.cpp: Disabled browser hardware acceleration by default
  to prevent GL context crashes on mobile drivers.
- frontend/cmake: Integrated custom system-info-termux.cpp to bypass
  SELinux PCI-bus scanning restrictions and adjusted Qt/Libpci linking.
